ghbour with a metal baseball bat for no reason, then making up a lie and getting away with it.<br \/>\nWe went inside and checked the Letter Box cam we had setup at the time and found that it was done by 2 people, The tenant of number 14 (which was obvious) and one of his henchmen (people that hang out with him for drugs).<br \/>\nThey made up a fake conversation claiming that someone in a balaclava had done it and run away, but even the police officer who listened to it didn&#8217;t believe that and advised us he&#8217;s more than likely making it up to cover his actions.<br \/>\nBecause the camera we used at the time couldn&#8217;t see anything more than the ground nothing was done, not even any questioning, he just got away with it again.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Video:<\/strong> (old LetterBox cam pointing at ground but has audio)<br \/>\n<video controls=\"controls\" width=\"600\" height=\"480\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;\" data-mce-type=\"bookmark\" class=\"mce_SELRES_start\">\ufeff<\/span><source src=\"\/videos\/10th%20January%202024%20DoorSmash.mp4\" type=\"video\/mp4\" \/><\/video><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Summery: on the 10th January 2024, we were out for Lucy&#8217;s Birthday, when we came home our front door window&#46;&#46;&#46;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":190,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[4,13,5,7,6],"tags":[10],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/192.168.0.108\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/181"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/192.168.0.108\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/192.168.0.108\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/192.168.0.108\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/192.168.0.108\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=181"}]